description: Demolition of Godwin and Wingfield Houses and ancillary garages in connection with the Estate Regeneration to provide 248 residential units within five new buildings of between 2-9 storeys and the retention of Tollgate House with associated external alterations, construction of a new single storey community centre and associated car parking, landscaping and open space.
